13. Monitoring Network Performance
Commands
Check Network Usage : iftop
Check Connections   : netstat
Check Routing Table : route -n

14. Shell Script Automation
Example script to monitor disk usage: #!/bin/bash df -h > disk_report.txt
Run: bash script.sh

15. Backup and Recovery
Backup Using tar : tar -cvf backup.tar /home
Restore : tar -xvf backup.tar
